<paragraph id="hd_id2501201615083017" role="heading" level="1" xml-lang="en-US">XML Source</paragraph>
<paragraph id="par_id2501201615083061" role="paragraph" xml-lang="en-US">The XML Source feature allows user to import data from arbitrarily structured XML content into cells in an existing spreadsheet document. It allows XML content to be imported either partially or in full, depending on the structure of the XML content and the map definitions that the user defines. The user can specify multiple non-overlapping sub-structures to be mapped to different cell positions within the same document. The user can import either element contents, attribute values or both.</paragraph>

